  "remarks": "EDBI Stock Brokerage Company is a subsidiary of the Export Development Bank of Iran (EDBI). It provides stock brokerage services to its customers. EDBI is a state-owned bank which provides support to the Government of Iran. Therefore, EDBI Stock Brokerage Company is owned or controlled by an entity providing support to the Government of Iran.",
